---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about HYCE Engineers & Infra â€“ a commercial construction firm serving for over 18 years with 30+ projects and 98% client satisfaction.">
  <!-- Page Banner -->
  <section class="page-banner">
    <div class="banner-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container banner-content">
      <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--color-gold);">Who We Are</span>
      <h1>About HYCE</h1>
      <p>Building excellence since 2005</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Intro -->
  <section class="about-intro">
    <div class="container intro-grid">
      <div class="intro-image">
        <img src="/images/hero/about-image.png" alt="HYCE Engineers & Infra - Commercial construction projects" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="intro-content">
        <span class="section-label">Who We Are</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Commercial construction firm serving for over 18 years.</h2>
        <p class="section-text">
          Founded in 2005, HYCE INFRA is a commercial construction firm dedicated to delivering quality projects on time and under budget. We specialize in new construction, renovation, and repurposing of existing structures, and currently serve clients spread all over Hyderabad.
        </p>
        <p class="section-text" style="margin-top: 16px;">
          Our team of experienced professionals brings a breadth of knowledge to every job, and our commitment to excellence ensures that the job is completed correctly and to the highest standards. We have been on the cutting edge of the industry for over 18 years.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
